OL,3,CFrom high-tech to human touch: Inside
OL,4,Ca critical care ward
OL,6,FWatch Helen Ford's special report into
OL,7,Fcritical care in a North East hospital
OL,8,Fon ITVX
OL,10,FSpotting a patient tucking into a
OL,11,Fhearty cooked breakfast was the last
OL,12,Fthing I had expected to see on
OL,13,Farriving at critical care.
OL,15,FIt was an early indication that - in a
OL,16,Fspecialist, high-tech environment
OL,17,Ftreating people with life-threatening
OL,18,Fconditions - there is also room for
OL,19,Fthe everyday.
