OL,3,CFrom high-tech to human touch: Inside
OL,4,Ca critical care ward
OL,6,FI was embarking on two days of filming
OL,7,Fon the critical care unit at the
OL,8,FNorthumbria Specialist Emergency Care
OL,9,FHospital, in Cramlington, shedding
OL,10,Flight on its work.
OL,12,FOne of the first things to strike me
OL,13,Fwas the mix of patients.
OL,15,FSome are admitted with serious medical
OL,16,Fconditions or physical injuries while
OL,17,Fothers are brought here following
OL,18,Fmajor surgery.
OL,20,FPatients may be here for 24 hours;
OL,21,Fothers for many weeks.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/10
