OL,3,CFrom high-tech to human touch: Inside
OL,4,Ca critical care ward
OL,6,FThe ages of those I met ranged from
OL,7,Ftheir 20s through to older people and
OL,8,Fwhile their situations varied, they
OL,9,Fwere united in relief - and
OL,10,Fthankfulness - for their treatment,
OL,11,Fwhich can be life-saving.
OL,13,FBecause of the seriousness of
OL,14,Fpatients' conditions, care is
OL,15,Fmonitored closely and precisely.
OL,17,FA nurse is allocated to a maximum of
OL,18,Ftwo patients, while those whose
OL,19,Fbreathing is supported by mechanical
OL,20,Fventilators receive one-to-one
OL,21,Fobservation.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/10
