OL,3,CFrom high-tech to human touch: Inside
OL,4,Ca critical care ward
OL,6,FIn this high stakes environment, as
OL,7,Fone nurse explained to me, it is vital
OL,8,Fto anticipate problems before they
OL,9,Farise.
OL,11,F10am sees the morning ward round,
OL,12,Fwhere the entire team visits each
OL,13,Fpatient's bedside to discuss their
OL,14,Ftreatment plan in detail.
OL,16,FIt is this gathering which underlines
OL,17,Fhow many staff - and disciplines -
OL,18,Fhave a role in critical care.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/10
