OL,3,CFrom high-tech to human touch: Inside
OL,4,Ca critical care ward
OL,6,FAlong with doctors, nurses and
OL,7,Fspecialist staff known as advanced
OL,8,Fcritical care practitioners, there are
OL,9,Fphysiotherapists, dieticians and
OL,10,Fpharmacists.
OL,12,FLater, I also meet a member of the
OL,13,FNorthumbria Healthcare trust alcohol
OL,14,Fcare team who is also a regular on the
OL,15,Funit.
OL,17,FIn recent years there has been a rise
OL,18,Fin admissions to critical care among
OL,19,Fpatients suffering the effects of
OL,20,Fdrugs and alcohol.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/10
