OL,3,CFrom high-tech to human touch: Inside
OL,4,Ca critical care ward
OL,6,FIn some cases, this can be due to a
OL,7,Fspecific incident - such as an
OL,8,Foverdose or alcohol poisoning.
OL,10,FOther patients, I was told, are living
OL,11,Fwith the long term impacts of drug and
OL,12,Falcohol use on their bodies.
OL,14,FThe alcohol care team aims to step in
OL,15,F- while patients are on critical care
OL,16,F- with support for them and their
OL,17,Ffamilies with the aim of reducing
OL,18,Ftheir dependence long term.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/10
