OL,3,CFrom high-tech to human touch: Inside
OL,4,Ca critical care ward
OL,6,FIt is fair to say that the very phrase
OL,7,F'critical care' can be frightening and
OL,8,Ffor the loved ones of patients in
OL,9,Fcritical care, these are anxious times.
OL,11,FWe see concern etched on the faces of
OL,12,Fvisitors who sit alongside patients'
OL,13,Fbeds.
OL,15,FBut this is also a very human
OL,16,Fenvironment and there is also
OL,17,Fconversation, reassuring smiles and
OL,18,Feven occasional laughter as families
OL,19,Ftry to stay positive.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/10
