OL,3,CFrom high-tech to human touch: Inside
OL,4,Ca critical care ward
OL,6,FFor me, the presence of these very
OL,7,Fhuman exchanges - between patients,
OL,8,Ffamilies and staff, provided some of
OL,9,Fthe most memorable moments of our time
OL,10,Fon the unit.
OL,12,FAs darkness falls, there is a
OL,13,Fnoticeable change of atmosphere on the
OL,14,Funit.
OL,16,FThe lights are dimmed and a quietness
OL,17,Fdescends.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/10
