OL,3,CFrom high-tech to human touch: Inside
OL,4,Ca critical care ward
OL,6,FOne nurse on the night shift explains
OL,7,Fto me the importance of allowing
OL,8,Fpatients to sleep well to aid their
OL,9,Frecovery.
OL,11,FFor this reason, he says, the aim is
OL,12,Fto keep disturbances to a minimum.
OL,14,FOf course, emergencies and new
OL,15,Fadmissions can happen at any time of
OL,16,Fday or night and staff must remain on
OL,17,Fthe highest alert; ever ready for any
OL,18,Feventuality.
OL,20,FHow do they do it?
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/10
