OL,3,CFrom high-tech to human touch: Inside
OL,4,Ca critical care ward
OL,6,FQuite apart from expertise -
OL,7,Fresilience and stamina, I was told,
OL,8,Fare essential qualities for anyone
OL,9,Fworking in this department.
OL,11,FThere is also another factor.
OL,13,FIn several conversations, staff
OL,14,Fdescribed the support they receive
OL,15,Ffrom each other as they carry out
OL,16,Ftheir challenging work.
OL,18,FIn the words of one of the nurses I
OL,19,Fspoke to: "We are a family."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G10/10
